snippet.title: Amber Heard, Janelle Monae front row at Valli
snippet.description:
A slanted wall with trapezoid-shaped window holes and sanitized lighting evoked the mood of a spaceship for Italian designer Giambattista Valli at his show in Paris. (March 5)
